From 88a1b9b1260e58266e9b6b687831065271ec4b90 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Ilya Gulya <ilya@gulya.me>
Date: Sun, 12 Jul 2026 15:54:11 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] darling: integrate rootless no-mount runtime

Consolidate startup, launchd bootstrap propagation, mldr argument/TSD setup, runtime component selection and the rootless bootstrap component.
---
